c2b","tid":2290076,"uid":31911,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f260f64d9454b78fbd77189a10858096e7b6233","tid":2290076,"uid":28524,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"每個成功嘅人都有一個伯樂，但你冇留意到千千萬萬個失敗嘅unlucky guys <br />\n但努力過嘅人永遠值得respect!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"太天真喇 你講果千千萬萬個unlucky guys畀佢有機會遇到周小姐（或者你講既伯樂）你估佢地就可以成功？<br />\n<br />\n要承認有啲層次係你幾努力都上唔到去 就好似你畀我有幾條命去努力都唔會上到Elon musk既層次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2950c85a1b9ae24944ad0e3b80e88d649d72b36d","tid":2290076,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T08:38:54.000Z","msg":"PROFILE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.horizonsventures.com/team/wayne-cheng/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.horizonsventures.com%2Fteam%2Fwayne-cheng%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1Sfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=3af3e689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.horizonsventures.com/team/wayne-cheng/</a>"}}